      • getThreadTracer

        public ThreadTracer getThreadTracer()
        Returns the ThreadTracer associated with the current (calling) thread. If no ThreadTracer exists so far, a new one is created, or a NullThreadTracer is returned if the Thread implements UntracedThread.
        Returns:
        the ThreadTracer associated with the current (calling) thread

      • wasRedefined

        public boolean wasRedefined(String className)
        Checks whether the class given by the fully qualified java class name has been redefined by the instrumenter or not. The classes that couldn't get redefined are those already loaded by the vm when the agent's premain method was executed.
        Parameters:
        className - the fully qualified classname to check
        Returns:
        true if the class was redefined, false if not
